{"tid":1768281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一諗到「人終有一死」，就由心底驚出黎？","createTime":"2019-12-04T03:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T04:05:36.000Z","uid":136306,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"50ad54e971d9f216b01c9ef0723b9a726250350b","tid":1768281,"uid":136306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"當你意識到人終有一死，意識到無論你做人做到幾成功，幾有錢，幾有名利都好，最後都要死。<br />\n<br />\n而死左之後，最正路應該就係乜感覺都冇，好似出世前咁。<br />\n<br />\n而你出世前，「一瞬間經歷」左138億光年既「虛無」，死後，就「一瞬間經歷」永遠既虛無。<br />\n<br />\n即係當你死左之後，你身邊既人都會死哂，人類絕種，地球比太陽吞噬左，銀河同銀河融合，宇宙萬物最終止於虛無。全部都「一瞬間」發生直到永永遠遠。<br />\n<br />\n以前既我會以為死係一種可能，只會發生係其他人身上。<br />\n<br />\n但其實，死係100%會發生自己身上。<br />\n<br />\n一諗到咁就好驚⋯⋯"},{"pid":"9050fed9da86cd1d37708aa85e74bbfb1e79ee64","tid":1768281,"uid":6111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"諗得透既話點解仲要驚？<br />\n死不嬲都唔可怕 可怕既係點死"},{"pid":"6722e51c68749be5a92edeb23d3f935506d48b5a","tid":1768281,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"唔明你講乜<br />\n但睇睇下都驚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac97ee5e1e3e6699c8766678e78cfb0fac4cfe6","tid":1768281,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:27:34.000Z","msg":"反而唔驚，因為所有人既終點都一樣"},{"pid":"0a46070d6694c6363b120a10cee8f1a688caea57","tid":1768281,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:28:18.000Z","msg":"所以要活得精彩"},{"pid":"7ef4239056594b878c5ed465d88e0c1430adaadb","tid":1768281,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:30:29.000Z","msg":"唔死咪仲慘，捱幾十年人仲未夠辛苦咩"},{"pid":"26bb432ecddb21bbf2a911f10b46fcae3d5f9dbb","tid":1768281,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:30:41.000Z","msg":"以前有 呢半年冇"},{"pid":"3cf305fb5ba9edab49bb7dc931ec40449a79b426","tid":1768281,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"打死一世工仲驚"},{"pid":"cbb79e293905da13f2999785d2a0f70d1e3e1c67","tid":1768281,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"c1c99041b7c4f331c8e1a1fec983dbda0b4e92d1","tid":1768281,"uid":140218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"初初諗會不安<br />\n諗多一千幾百次就會無乜感覺"},{"pid":"b4f05c6ce9fe4cb522207a5d45b58d8b0e786427","tid":1768281,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:41:43.000Z","msg":"我調返轉<br />\n呢年之前仲會諗世界安排我廿一世紀出世<br />\n係等我可以見證到長生不老既科技誕生<br />\n不過今年發生太多事 令我無辦法唔想像現實 跟住呢幾個月我都好驚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9d8f88e9f49270af5009454e297e8cf20a5156","tid":1768281,"uid":332877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9050fed9da86cd1d37708aa85e74bbfb1e79ee64","tid":1768281,"uid":6111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"諗得透既話點解仲要驚？<br />\n死不嬲都唔可怕 可怕既係點死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:42:35.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"d4fdff72f75ece9db55e9fabe08297ecf2480071","tid":1768281,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">日程表</span></span></strong><br />\n－－－－－－<strong><em>和理非合法活動集合</em></strong>－－－－－－</div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期五 12 &middot; 6 </span><br />\n「吸吸可危」抵禦催淚彈集會</strong></span><br />\n- 19:00 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1766230/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1766230/page/1</a><br />\n<br